A highly detailed cinematic digital artwork of a mysterious ronin samurai standing in a dark, misty forest at night. The figure wears traditional black samurai robes and a wide conical straw hat (kasa) with glowing neon-orange outlines tracing the brim and edges, emitting a soft futuristic glow. His face is partially obscured by shadow and long braided hair strands hanging down. He holds a drawn katana in a ready stance, the blade replaced by a bright glowing orange energy sword with neon circuits and holographic spirals along the guard and hilt, radiating intense orange light that illuminates his torso and hands.
Composition: Vertical portrait, low-angle shot looking slightly up to emphasize power and menace, centered figure dominating the frame, dramatic rim lighting from the neon elements against deep black shadows.
Atmosphere: Dark, moody, cyberpunk-fantasy fusion, foggy background with blurred silhouettes of trees, high contrast, mysterious and intense.
Color palette: Predominantly desaturated blacks and grays with strong vibrant neon orange accents as the only light source, creating a glowing ember effect.
Style: Hyper-realistic digital art blended with cyberpunk neon aesthetics, intricate details on fabrics and braids, subtle particle effects from the glowing elements, inspired by Ghost of Tsushima meets Blade Runner.
